{"tid":1931786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三招對抗藍絲文宣戰","createTime":"2020-03-18T10:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T12:21:17.000Z","uid":306340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8a733ebe5ae998473010130065c98633abbf89","tid":1931786,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"Source : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B93vz2inXVg/?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB93vz2inXVg%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_button_share_sheet&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=62ee95c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB93vz2inXVg%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_button_share_sheet&h=26b17a49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B93vz2inXVg/?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet</a><br />\n跳到結論，先講重點。<br />\n<br />\n1. 停止恥笑外國人<br />\n2. 加強專業醫學文宣<br />\n3. 集中輿論講23條<br />\n<br />\n入正題。消失一段時間，整理了藍營的媒體策略。<br />\n<br />\n簡言之，中國信奉借力打力，而且極其有效。<br />\n<br />\n今天講講藍營幾大文宣方向。<br />\n<br />\n【一：殺了你媽，就歌頌你爸】<br />\n<br />\n殺死你老竇之後，讚你老母含辛茹苦養大你，宣揚母愛偉大。<br />\n<br />\n這就是中國式文宣。<br />\n<br />\n記住，藍營媒體戰，主體就是轉移焦點。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎令全球失陷（Well，台灣還好），中國境內是重災區。<br />\n<br />\n由一月開始，黨媒發功，吹奏醫護人員盡忠職守，捨身救人。藍絲一片掌聲，側寫香港醫護罷工，是黑護暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n中國多好。<br />\n<br />\n同理，武肺於國際爆發，黨媒發放「新聞」，指意大利市民播中國國歌，感謝中國救援。<br />\n<br />\n中共從來思想積極。現在嘛，既然感染了全球，就做拯救世界的英雄唄。<br />\n<br />\n有肺炎，不提源頭，只講成功案例；<br />\n醫護死，不改體制，只講偉大精神；<br />\n全球爆，不肯道歉，自捧英雄救世。<br />\n<br />\n國際線與香港文宣，基本上一樣打法。你會笑，但總有人受。<br />\n<br />\n買通世衛的譚得塞，就是為了控制官方口徑，按套路引導輿論。<br />\n<br />\n那些信眾，就是我們的對立面。<br />\n<br />\nclick 入 link 去睇全文，支持黃色媒體人"},{"pid":"b91f8e8c413635e323e067dfc4fe77ba7263d254","tid":1931786,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acc336a0119c1f0172e17d7bebbc8e9f98a32fe","tid":1931786,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"少d笑人 多個同路人"},{"pid":"a168c553c58a96c8c5e7b4605d36f07a4f8488b1","tid":1931786,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f6007b7b72e2abc9832b523ec813f037b5fb85","tid":1931786,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"推"}]}